These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, january
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, singing
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, blue
City: venice, miami
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, thai
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person who likes apricot##8
3. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person traveling to venice##6
4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
5. the person who likes blue is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8
6. the thai is not the person driving the roller##6
7. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | coffee      |
| Birthday          | january | august   |
| Hobby         | singing    | board-games |
| Color           | apricot     | blue    |
| City   | miami    | venice       |
| Nationality   | italian    | thai        |
| Transport     | roller     | tram        |

